OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,FFirst time voters in the UK's
OL,7,F"youngest city" have shared their
OL,8,Fthoughts ahead of the upcoming
OL,9,Felections.
OL,11,FWith around 29% of its half a million
OL,12,Fresidents aged under 20 - and nearly a
OL,13,Fquarter under 16 - Bradford has the
OL,14,Fyoungest population of any city in the
OL,15,Fcountry.
OL,17,FAnd, as the academic year comes to a
OL,18,Fclose at the University of Bradford,
OL,19,Fstudents on the AI and future
OL,20,Ftechnologies course are looking at
OL,21,Fwhat their future might bring.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
