CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778217988
OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,FITV Calendar attended the university's
OL,7,F2026 computer showcase to speak to
OL,8,Fstudents who will head to the polls
OL,9,Ffor the first time on Thursday as
OL,10,Flocal elections take place.
OL,12,FThe city's council has been Labour-
OL,13,Fcontrolled for more than a decade, but
OL,14,Ftheir majority is now just a single
OL,15,Fseat and this all out election could
OL,16,Fsee a significant shift in the
OL,17,Fauthority's political makeup.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
