FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778217988
OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,FHasan Akhtar is 21 years-old and
OL,7,Fvoting for the first time. He believes
OL,8,Fit is important that young people vote
OL,9,Fto ensure they are reflected in the
OL,10,Fpolls.
OL,12,FThe BSC computer science student said:
OL,13,F"The votes need to be a representation
OL,14,Fof everyone, so if fewer young people
OL,15,Fare voting then the representation
OL,16,Fwon't be captured as much."
OL,18,FFor Barirah Irfan, who is also 21 and
OL,19,Fin her final year, apathy towards
OL,20,Fpolitics as a whole put her off voting
OL,21,Fin previous elections.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778217988
OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,FShe said: "I think last time round
OL,7,Fthere was just a lack of motivation -
OL,8,Fthe sense that will my vote even count
OL,9,Ftowards anything?
OL,11,F"I don't even remember doing enough
OL,12,Fresearch on it, so I just thought
OL,13,Fwhat's the point. "
OL,15,FHowever Barirah, who comes from
OL,16,FBradford and is searching for jobs in
OL,17,Fand around her home city, is hoping
OL,18,Fher vote can help address issues that
OL,19,Fare important to her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778217988
OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,F"I think the main thing is just the
OL,7,Fjob market in general," she said.
OL,8,F"It's incredibly hard for young people
OL,9,Ffresh out of uni.
OL,11,F"So I think a lot of people just want
OL,12,Fto vote to get that main point
OL,13,Faddressed."
OL,15,FOver two thirds of UK-based
OL,16,Fundergraduate students at the
OL,17,Funiversity live at home while studying.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
