PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778217988
OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,FJustyna Dobersztajn, who was raised in
OL,7,Fthe city, hadn't previously
OL,8,Facknowledged the influence that
OL,9,Fpolitics can have.
OL,11,FThe 26-year-old said: "I never got an
OL,12,Feducation regarding politics. I never
OL,13,Fknew what influence I can have, how it
OL,14,Finfluences me in the real world, and
OL,15,Fthe impact that I can have by voting."
OL,17,FAfter starting university and doing
OL,18,Fher own research into the different
OL,19,Fparties Justyna has also encouraged
OL,20,Fher family to vote as well.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778217988
OL,3,CThe first-time voters in 'youngest
OL,4,Ccity' hoping others will have their say
OL,6,F"My family didn't vote either, so we
OL,7,Fall started looking into it and
OL,8,Fstarted getting more interested and
OL,9,Fhaving little debates at home.
OL,11,F"This year we have decided to all go
OL,12,Fout and go and vote for the first time
OL,13,Fas a family."
OL,15,FJustyna hopes other young people will
OL,16,Falso take to the polls. She said: "I
OL,17,Fam going for the first time, so I hope
OL,18,Fother people will as well."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
